    a fabio:JournalArticle .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8292253>
    dc:description "Fig. 1. The petal blight of R. agastum. (A) R. agastum grown in field habitat. (B) The healthy flower of R. agastum. (C) The petal blight flower of R. agastum (white arrow)." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8292253/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8292255>
    dc:description "Fig. 2. Total ion current (TIC) chromatogram of healthy flowers (HF) and petal blight flowers (PBF) of R. agastum using GC-TOF-MS." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8292255/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.8292257>
    dc:description "Fig. 3. The data analysis of the metabolites based on GC-TOF-MS in the healthy flowers and petal blight flowers of R. agastum. (A) Principal component analysis (PCA). (B) Orthogonal projections to latent structures discriminant analysis (OPLS-DA). The green and red circles display 95% confidence regions of petal blight and healthy flowers. (For interpretation of the references to color in this figure legend, the reader is referred to the Web version of this article.)" ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/8292257/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

